show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: Left for dead by his own brother, he refuses to let fate have the final say. When his true power resurfaces, he faces corrupt masters, ruthless fighters, and the demons within. A gripping tale of revenge, redemption, and the rebirth of a legend.
